"The |legend| :guilabel:`Legend` tab provides you with advanced settings for "
"the :ref:`Layers panel <label_legend>` and/or the :ref:`print layout legend "
"<layout_legend_item>`. These options include:"
msgstr ""
"தி |புராணக்கதை| :guilabel:`Legend` தாவல் :ref:`Layers panel <label_legend>` "
